messages.speech: We are one of the top 200 publicly traded companies in Asia, and a member of the Fortune 500.
Through our businesses, we provide high-quality products, services and experiences to increasingly prosperous and digitally-connected consumers and businesses across Asia.

We are a major investor in a unique portfolio of industry-leading businesses spanning a wide range of sectors including premium property, first-rate motors, modern retail, world-class hotels and state-of-the-art engineering and construction.
Diversity is our strength but what unifies our group of companies is a singular focus and purpose: to enhance the quality of life of Asia’s consumers.
